room_title: Escape room "Totally 80’s" by Time Escape Loveland in Fort Collins
room_description: Gag me with a spoon, it's like totally the 80’s....(righteous!), and you have scored primo tickets to the biggest concert of the summer, Michael Jackson’s “Bad” tour. Total bummer though: you don't know where you put them and you’re wigging out! You book it to your friend Heather's house but not only are the tickets missing, so is Heather's whole family. Barf me out!
